# 🔥 TCS SHORTCUT QUESTION

## Example 1

A shop gives 20% discount on ₹500.

Find selling price.

### Solution Shortcut:

20% of 500:

[
\frac{20}{100} \times 500 = 100
]

SP:

[
500 - 100 = 400
]

✅ Answer = ₹400

